  "metadata": {
    "what_it_measures": "Average hourly earnings for all private employees. BLS, released with NFP on 1st Friday. AHE YoY is the key wage inflation number.\n",
    "why_it_matters": "Wages drive services inflation. AHE above 3.5% YoY makes the Fed's 2% inflation target difficult. Baumohl Tier 1 component of NFP report.\n",
    "scoring_rule": "YoY: < 3.0% \u2192 +60 | 3.0-3.5% \u2192 +20 | 3.5-4.0% \u2192 -20 | 4.0-5.0% \u2192 -50 | > 5.0% \u2192 -80. Phase 3.\n"
  },
